    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Wulandari Bangun Laksana Tbk engages in the real estate business in Indonesia. The company operates through Developer, Pentacity Mall, E-walk Mall, Estate Management, and Other segments. Its Developer segment is involved in the sale apartment units, condotels, and shop houses and rental of malls, hotels, and office spaces. The Pentacity Mall segment provides management services in the Pentacity mall area of Balikpapan. Its E-walk Mall segment offers management services in the Balikpapan E-walk mall area. The Estate Management segment provides management services in the Balikpapan Superblock area. Its Other segment offers fitness, waterpark rides, and food court management services. The company also operates a health clinic and Bina Bangsa School, as well as recreational places, entertainment, hotels, and shopping centers. The company was formerly known as PT Dwi Pagria Lesatari and changed its name to PT Wulandari Bangun Laksana Tbk in April 2002. PT Wulandari Bangun Laksana Tbk was founded in 1994 and is based in Balikpapan, Indonesia.",
